        public int predictedRankingPoints()
        Predicts the number of ranking points at the end of qualifications using the actual ranking points from the completed matches and predicting ranking points acquired from the remaining ones. Note: Currently set up based on 2 for wins, 1 for ties, and 0 for loses. Additional RP will need to be added.
        Returns:
        predicted number of ranking points at the end of qualifications
